", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>向市场监管部门投诉或提起民事诉讼</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>纠集亲友到平台公司示威</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>&nbsp;自认倒霉不再追究</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<p>在网络散布平台诈骗信息</p>\n"}], "prompt": "<p>（改编）某平台“盲盒抽奖”诱导未成年人充值万元，家长维权可优先选择（　）</p>\n", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "5136342960", "44bec67a-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "$RE0000", "$M003002000", "ff8080814371757b014390f883db0453", "5036342749", "$RE0200", "6a74973a-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "$RE0201", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "5136342960", "44bec67a-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "ff8080814371757b014390f883db0453", "6a74973a-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5"], "status": "ONLINE", "is_publish": false, "id": "c4c9391b-e69d-4c4b-9c57-24858ecc05f4", "global_title": {"zh-CN": "（改编）某平台“盲盒抽奖”诱导未成年人充值万元，家长维权可优先选择（　）"}, "global_description": {"zh-CN": "<p>（改编）某平台“盲盒抽奖”诱导未成年人充值万元，家长维权可优先选择（　）</p>\n"}, "global_keywords": {}, "global_label": {}, "custom_properties": {"sys_packing_status": "ready", "preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/c4c9391b-e69d-4c4b-9c57-24858ecc05f4@1.pkg/1772597634102/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597634762", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/c4c9391b-e69d-4c4b-9c57-24858ecc05f4@1.pkg/1772597634102/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597634762"}, "auto_fill_thumb": true, "